      "speakerName": "サヤ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saya",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "どうも～。びっくりしましたよ、まさかあの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hi there~. I was surprised. To think that",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.9149885337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "サヤ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saya",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-saya001.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4のサニピのお二人がいるなんて～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "the two of you from Sunny Peace‚ a BIG4 group‚ are here~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.2483216603,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 19.7816567262
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "お手柔らかにお願いしますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please go easy on us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.7816567262,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 22.395080471
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（この人達……最近ライブバトルで連勝中で）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（These girls… They’ve been on a winning streak in live battles recently‚）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.395080471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "（話題になってるグループの人だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（and they’re the group that’s been the talk of the town.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.4617454051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 30.2054658571
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "アヤ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aya",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-aya001.m4a",
      "text": "それにしてもびっくりだよね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s so surprising‚ don’t you think~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.2054658571,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "アヤ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aya",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "「あの」佐伯遙子さんが今やBIG4なんて～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“That” Haruko Saeki is now in the BIG4~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.7284120718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 40.3721322695
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "……どういう意味ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.3721322695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "アヤ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aya",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だって、あの頃はもういるかどうかも分かんない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ back then‚ she had such a small presence",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.3649438698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "アヤ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aya",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-aya002.m4a",
      "text": "くらい存在感なかったもんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "that you couldn’t tell if she was even there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.9950764496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "サヤ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saya",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-saya002.m4a",
      "text": "ソロで冴えなくても、良さげなグループさえ組めば",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If a solo career doesn’t work out‚ you can just form a decent group",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.6649377663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "サヤ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saya",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "売れちゃうんだから……運がいいよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and become popular… She’s so lucky.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 61.2649377663
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……何を勝手なこと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Don’t talk nonsense…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.2649377663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "あなた達に遙子さんの何が分かって――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you know about Haruko-san――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.028409783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 67.2773871898
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "怜ちゃん、それ以上言わなくていいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei‚ you don’t have to say anything more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.2773871898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "言いたい人には言わせておけばいいのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just let them say whatever they want.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 73.5877725759
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "遙子さん！？　でも……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san!? But…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.5877725759,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "こんなこと言われて悔しくないんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aren’t you angry after hearing something like that!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.1721285024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 80.6481579619
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私が売れてなかったのは事実だしね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s true that I wasn’t popular‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.6481579619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "地味で存在感ないのも自覚はあるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and I’m aware that I’m plain and have no presence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 87.6069331643
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "サヤ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saya",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-saya003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ？　なになに、寛容アピールの上に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? What‚ after acting all tolerant‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.6069331643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "サヤ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saya",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "自虐で可愛らしさアピールですか～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "now you’re trying to appear cute by putting yourself down~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.1642370381,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 98.6069316384
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……いい加減にして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Enough is enough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.6069316384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんをバカにするのは、私が許さない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won’t forgive you for making fun of Haruko-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.9642370381,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今ここで宣言するわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m making a declaration here and now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.8757067836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "あなた達も倒して、私と遙子さんが優勝する！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll defeat you‚ and Haruko-san and I will win this tournament!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.0975703714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 114.2191531972
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "アヤ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aya",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "へ～、宣言とかかっこい～。確かにサニピはBIG4に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa‚ a declaration? So cool. Sure‚ Sunny Peace might be in the BIG4‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.2191531972,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "アヤ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aya",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-aya003.m4a",
      "text": "なったけど、五人揃ってるからこその強さでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but their strength comes from having all five members together‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.0309037047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 128.9524865307
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "サヤ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saya",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あんた達二人だけなら、負ける気がしないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it’s just the two of you‚ I don’t think we’ll lose.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.9524865307,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "サヤ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saya",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-saya004.m4a",
      "text": "実際に戦ってみれば分かるわよ。それじゃ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ll see when we actually battle. Later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.5308986185,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3335.768048200009
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
